=== SILICON_SCHOLARS ===
# id: 32
# title: The Silicon Scholars
# chinese_title: 硅晶学者
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

Three beings of living silicon sit in a circle, projecting holographic equations between them. They pause as you enter and rotate their featureless faces toward you. One projects a simple mathematical puzzle, clearly an invitation to prove your intelligence.

* [Solve their mathematical puzzle]
  ~ gain_radical("大")
  "大" (dà) — big, great
* [Present a puzzle of your own]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "题" (tí) — problem, question, topic
* [Offer technology in exchange for knowledge] {requires: gold >= 15}
  ~ gain_radical("石")
  "石" (shí) — stone, mineral
* [Observe silently and take notes]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "看" (kàn) — to look, to watch
